item.title: How this site was created...
item.description: This is my first blog post which I created mostly to test out how the blog would work if we decided to have one. This website is a draft for testing out options for posting accessible data tables and reports for CUNY’s Office of Institutional Research. This site was created using RStudio and blogdown using the default blogdown/Hugo theme, hugo-lithium, as a base and then customizing it to be more in line with CUNY’s branding by altering the layouts and CSS.
